    âœ”ï¸ Follow the Principle of Least Privilege â€“ Grant only the necessary permissions.
    âœ”ï¸ Use Lifecycle Policies â€“ Move old data to cheaper storage classes.
    âœ”ï¸ Enable Logging â€“ Monitor access using AWS CloudTrail.
